column4: ah WPax, your hajopolis station is somewhat crowded :D
The numbers arre decreasing ever so slowly now...
Well, I jammed up half of knittern for a few years ;)
No pax out = no pax in
Hi All. What are the settings for bankrupcy? I may have overspent...
Heh. I turned on freeplay by mistake... so you're good
But timothy will fix it sometime, so beware, you'll be liquidated when he does.
Excellent. I'm making money, so hopefully it'll give me enough time!
Do you want a pax interchange near Stonebridge?
Well, my net wealth is positive
southpax i can give you a boost if you let me build a public airport near one of your cities
A Pax internchange west of Guttstart would be good (by the canal).
Public needs to build my platform at West Guttstart Interchange. If I do it blds a new station
"make station public" in special construction toolbar
But I can do it to save you a bit of cash. how many tiles?
Okay, you're hooked up to the network!
Cool. We'll see what that does for the bank balance!
Once you get interconnected, profit skyrockets. I have a margin over 87% right now!
I've made an interchange near chickchester, under the highway bridge
When your network reaches chickchester connect your trains to the station
So we'll both have huigher profits
East Pax: 2x tunnels still for deletion at 675,373 I think
You can remove the taxiway alone, did you try?
There, removed, taxiway at 417,394/7 for you
Thanks. I hadn't tried, as it wasn't mine. Good to know though!
South pax, may I ask what you're doing in knittern?
Well I noticed this little passenger network appeared on my side of the green line south of Kittern, as allowed by the red zone on the map, so I thought fair's fair!
I think all of knittern is in my zone by that map (at least that is how I intended when I drew the map
If you want, you can have *all* of my network, I actually like freight better...
Well, you've got quite the bus network going by your station!!
What's the red dotted zone on the map all about then?
*rolleyes* Those are definitely buses serving thoe farms...
Okay, so what? I remove farm busses and you remove trains?
WestPax: Your network looks stable, surely you could just leave it and switch to freight?
So do you want it or should I just leave it open to another player?
Leave it open. Do you want me to remove the trains?
Because there's 8k passengers at your station, I don't see it's causing a problem.
I'd like you to, yes. I need to fix the pax system for interchange. I'll get rid of the busses.
I think you should keep them, that's the odd thing. I can't get passengers to there, they all come from Kittern.
I'll keep it if you want...
I think we can just chalk this up to we both should have asked permission first...
I think so! Why don't you add me a platform at Kittern Station and I'll divert my trains into that?
*note to self* demolish tunnels is expensive!!
*note to self* demolishing tunnels is expensive!
Yes, because all tunnels are 280 km/h!
I'm logging off now, I'll let the bank account recover a bit!
